Description: Carhartt Legacy Wheeled Gear Traveler 25 inch Brown Let's face it, your trips don't include hot towels or complimentary cocktails and you need luggage that understands that. Travel with confidence no matter where you're headed with the Carhartt Legacy Wheeled Gear Traveler. Built of heavy-duty 1200D Poly with Rain Defender durable water repellent and Duravax abrasion-resistant base this bag can handle any rough and tough conditions being on the road may bring. The Gear Traveler is available in 3 sizes - 21 inch (carry-on), 25 inch, 28 inch - each boast a large main compartment with multiple interior pockets plus a secondary shoe compartment for when you need to keep items separated.
